                        116)

that
                    the candidate is eligible to be nominated as a candidate for a constituency;
                    or

the nomination form has not been signed by the prescribed number of
                    subscribers qualified to subscribe to the nomination form under the District
                    Councils (Subscribers and Election Deposit for Nomination) Regulation (Cap. 547 sub. leg. A);

subparagraph.content:
whether the candidate is eligible to be nominated as a candidate under
                        the District Councils Ordinance (Cap. 547);
                        and

paragraph.content:
whether the candidate has been nominated for another constituency in the
